headline.main: What if There's No Affordable Insurance to Buy?
headline.print_headline: What if There's No Affordable Insurance to Buy?

lead_paragraph: Leslie Kurtz needed three plates, eight screws and a big assist from her insurer after breaking every bone in her ankle while white water rafting.
